snippet.title: Princess Rescue - Mario Atari 2600 Homebrew
snippet.description:
This is a very cool homebrew game made by Chris Spry over at (I beleive) Atari Age. Considering the limitations of the Atari 2600, this game gets really close to Mario 1 style gameplay. 

I believe this is the origin / homepage for the game. If there is a more official place please let me know:
https://atariage.com/forums/topic/215058-princess-rescue-binaries-released/

Big thanks to Chris Spry for creating and releasing this fun game and Atari Age for publishing it!
